Review Text:
I ordered food, they sent rumali roti instead of tanduri , also curries were full of thin oil every other item was just dipped in that oil.
Not tasty, neither healthy, wont recommend.
I ordered biryani for my friend and he was compleatly disapointed with the single and small pieces in it,rice quantity was good but i didnt order for plain rice
I have tried biriyani there it was so bad in test...rice is totally hard and chicken is not proper cooked....wrost biriyani i have tried ever....

I Ordered one Single Chiken Biryani, rice quality & quantity  is good. But the taste was worst!. I don't feel like I'm having Hyderabadi Biryani.  So much turmeric powder smell . no taste at all. I will never Order from Maharaja again!.. :(
For the 1st time I have ordered from this hotel and the mutton curry was awesome 👏👌👌👌the way of packing is too good and the taste was very good

Great food & taste... Best in all chicken and non -veg items...
Biryani is awesome like chicken, egg and other rice.
Paneer butter masala...
Recommend for all people!!!

I placed order for the starter chilli chicken after midnight. Usually for sides. The quantity was good however the pieces were bit hard. Taste is ok type. And one more thing they cook the food as per our customization (we preferred without curry leaves), and voila!
Not bad, had good experience with the food. 👍
Excellent biryani. Delicious food. Available round the clock . Special dining for family is also available. Management is very good. Nice experience .
